Talent Acquisition Specialist
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/30 11:04:51
Ref. JB3045800
Job Description
Being part of the Corporate HR Team, the Talent Acquisition Specialist
will be responsible for recruitment across all functions/businesses within the Group. Duties include, but not limited to,
• Interact actively with line managers in defining qualifications and attributes of potential hires.
• Construct and implement recruitment plan and identify appropriate sources to attract qualified candidates.
• Coordinate and conduct interviews as required.
• Assure all hiring is done in compliance with regulatory requirements.
• Conduct on-boarding of new hires and assist with new hire orientation when required.
• Designing and managing the careers page of the company website
• Managing the Linkedin account and other social media avenues
• Actively supporting the company’s Emiratisation drive
Skills
Education:
•	Degree/Diploma in Human Resources.
Experience:
•	At least 5 years talent acquisition/recruitment experience with a combination of in-house and external search.
Qualifications:
•	Well versed in sourcing candidates for multiple disciplines/industries.
•	Proven record of closing middle and senior management positions.
•	Experience with varied sourcing strategies including portals, ads, consultants, social networking, headhunting etc.
•	Comfortable with working in a multinational environment.
•	Knowledge of recruitment software
