About This Company
Galadari Brothers Group is one amongst the large and well known Business Conglomerates in the U.A.E. The Group comprises of companies operating in various sectors that include Automobiles, Industrial Trading, Media, Retail, Engineering, Hospitality, Real Estate, IT, Travel and Tourism. With operations across the GCC the Group plans to cut across geographical boundaries by investing in business opportunities that increase shareholder value.As pioneers in the business segments the Group operates in, it reflects the dynamism of the U.A.E and vision to continue growing with the Country. The Group's presence in the most vibrant sectors of the UAE economy is the main fortitude which would not have been possible without the human capital of the Companies.
